{"tid":2052264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去到某個年紀就謝絕一切試圖令自己好過既野","createTime":"2020-06-05T11:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T12:16:45.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae34e6ddf23e072e49eddc45921d5217158a1f0","tid":2052264,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"因為知道只係暫時<br />\n好似食白粉咁<br />\n過後又要面對深層次矛盾<br />\n而你知依d矛盾係冇可能消弭<br />\n一係呃自己<br />\n一係麻醉自己<br />\n經歷得多<br />\n去到某個年紀<br />\n連呃自己麻醉自己亦費事<br />\n一黎終於知冇用<br />\n二黎慣左<br />\n同埋始終自己都大<br />\n冇以前咁錫身<br />\n或者可以咁講<br />\n而家做人<br />\n甚至開始覺得<br />\n連令自己唔好咁難受<br />\n盡量將生存痛苦減至最低<br />\n原來亦唔易<br />\n你命中註定要受苦<br />\n只可以痛到死為止"},{"pid":"097f952db74c2ce1017ffca19f908cc4c8980778","tid":2052264,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"打完丁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049751c9a0699b828daf81cd20bc02da91e9d1f2","tid":2052264,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097f952db74c2ce1017ffca19f908cc4c8980778","tid":2052264,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"打完丁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"賢者模式"},{"pid":"9e4f847572ede7ec9069b3af3e2f1ec9cd4dbef3","tid":2052264,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097f952db74c2ce1017ffca19f908cc4c8980778","tid":2052264,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"打完丁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"伍兄有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}